### Enrichment
Classic Southern banana pudding uses layers of vanilla pudding, sliced bananas, and Nilla wafers with whipped cream or meringue. Two approaches: no-cook (condensed milk, cream cheese, instant pudding) or from-scratch (homemade custard with meringue). Key tip: Nilla Wafers hold up better than generic brands. Refrigerate 4+ hours. Serves 10-12 in a 9x13 dish. Paula Deen version is extremely popular.

